text: You know a song is epic and perfectly cheesy when it's composed and sung by the Follin brothers, lasting for 7 minutes. You even have your typical instrumental break in the middle, a very solid one at that. The game itself is your standard beat 'em up, but I'm sure it must have been hard to press Start with such a theme song. He's gonna get himself some justiiiiice.
